--- goal of the game ---
space race:
    - be the first one into space
    - build your rocket and successfully launch it before the other party


--- full rules for this game ---
- object of the game is to be the first one to build and launch rocket
- turn system the same as base
- rocket progress is based on pts; more pts = more progress
- when a rocket is built and ready for launch, a launch card must be drawn and played.
    - if the launch card is SUCCESS then the player wins.
    - if the launch card is FAILURE then the player loses progress.

